he is struggling. Wow physics is fun i want
to try it Spidy. Okay i think i get it Mass

can you please get off me i seriously cant

breath. haha. Hey everyone how about you all
give it a try that way you can all learn better.

Spidy come on you promised me I give up. Mass
is my fist. Ouch. I love this new school.

Oh oh. Ouch. My fist is them mass and oh.

That was great. Come on Goblin get up your

getting smushed by a girl a little girl. Here

Mr. Gobby. for your great volunteer work.
Uh i can't stand you Spiderman uh. Alright

class our next subject will be. *bell* Well,
I guess the school day is over, see ya. Annabelle

that would be totally awesome. Why don't you
come over and play at our house? yea, I want

Yea we have lots of toys. yay toys yea. Click

on the screen to see Krista play Amber and
Annabelle's on the All Toy Collector channel.
Thanks for watching and have a great day!
